{
  "video_id": "iPxg6bRgPhE",
  "title": "Bandi Mbubi: Demand a fair trade cell phone",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16407.0,
      "end_time": 18346.0,
      "text": "I want to talk to you today"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18370.0,
      "end_time": 21633.0,
      "text": "about a difficult topic that is close to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21657.0,
      "end_time": 24742.0,
      "text": "and closer than you might realize to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26313.0,
      "end_time": 31595.0,
      "text": "I came to the UK 21 years ago, as an asylum-seeker."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32305.0,
      "end_time": 33599.0,
      "text": "I was 21."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34210.0,
      "end_time": 38650.0,
      "text": "I was forced to leave the Democratic Republic of the Congo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38890.0,
      "end_time": 41207.0,
      "text": "my home, where I was a student activist."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 44960.0,
      "end_time": 47934.0,
      "text": "I would love my children to be able to meet my family in the Congo."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 51355.0,
      "end_time": 55890.0,
      "text": "But I want to tell you what the Congo has got to do with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 56481.0,
      "end_time": 60209.0,
      "text": "But first of all, I want you to do me a favor."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 60549.0,
      "end_time": 65826.0,
      "text": "Can you all please reach into your pockets and take out your mobile phone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 69790.0,
      "end_time": 71800.0,
      "text": "Feel that familiar weight ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 73683.0,
      "end_time": 76850.0,
      "text": "how naturally your finger slides towards the buttons."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 76874.0,
      "end_time": 79660.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 80740.0,
      "end_time": 82253.0,
      "text": "Can you imagine your world without it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 82277.0,
      "end_time": 84761.0,
      "text": "It connects us to our loved ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 84785.0,
      "end_time": 88404.0,
      "text": "our family, friends and colleagues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 88428.0,
      "end_time": 91210.0,
      "text": "at home and overseas."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 91450.0,
      "end_time": 93783.0,
      "text": "It is a symbol of an interconnected world."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 95618.0,
      "end_time": 101440.0,
      "text": "But what you hold in your hand leaves a bloody trail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 101464.0,
      "end_time": 104222.0,
      "text": "and it all boils down to a mineral:"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 105349.0,
      "end_time": 109360.0,
      "text": "tantalum, mined in the Congo as coltan."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 109676.0,
      "end_time": 112573.0,
      "text": "It is an anticorrosive heat conductor."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 113176.0,
      "end_time": 119457.0,
      "text": "It stores energy in our mobile phones, PlayStations and laptops."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 120760.0,
      "end_time": 125791.0,
      "text": "It is used in aerospace and medical equipment as an alloy."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 126370.0,
      "end_time": 130492.0,
      "text": "It is so powerful that we only need tiny amounts."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 131603.0,
      "end_time": 134684.0,
      "text": "It would be great if the story ended there."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 135469.0,
      "end_time": 139123.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, what you hold in your hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 139147.0,
      "end_time": 144859.0,
      "text": "has not only enabled incredible technological development"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 144884.0,
      "end_time": 147716.0,
      "text": "and industrial expansion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 147741.0,
      "end_time": 152483.0,
      "text": "but it has also contributed to unimaginable human suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 153348.0,
      "end_time": 156550.0,
      "text": "Since 1996,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 156790.0,
      "end_time": 161749.0,
      "text": "over five million people have died in the Democratic Republic of the Congo."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 162298.0,
      "end_time": 169950.0,
      "text": "Countless women, men and children have been raped, tortured or enslaved."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 170336.0,
      "end_time": 173139.0,
      "text": "Rape is used as a weapon of war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 173163.0,
      "end_time": 177972.0,
      "text": "instilling fear and depopulating whole areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 178639.0,
      "end_time": 182586.0,
      "text": "The quest for extracting this mineral"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 182610.0,
      "end_time": 187269.0,
      "text": "has not only aided, but it has fueled"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 187293.0,
      "end_time": 190950.0,
      "text": "the ongoing war in the Congo."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 192535.0,
      "end_time": 194886.0,
      "text": "But don&#39;t throw away your phones yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 195929.0,
      "end_time": 200150.0,
      "text": "Thirty thousand children are enlisted"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 200390.0,
      "end_time": 203189.0,
      "text": "and are made to fight in armed groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 205418.0,
      "end_time": 209375.0,
      "text": "The Congo consistently scores dreadfully"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 209399.0,
      "end_time": 212435.0,
      "text": "in global health and poverty rankings."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 213927.0,
      "end_time": 215380.0,
      "text": "But remarkably,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 215404.0,
      "end_time": 221100.0,
      "text": "the UN Environmental Programme has estimated the wealth of the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 221124.0,
      "end_time": 226167.0,
      "text": "to be over 24 trillion dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 231286.0,
      "end_time": 235145.0,
      "text": "The state-regulated mining industry has collapsed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 235169.0,
      "end_time": 238834.0,
      "text": "and control over mines has splintered."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 238858.0,
      "end_time": 242306.0,
      "text": "Coltan is easily controlled by armed groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 243306.0,
      "end_time": 248490.0,
      "text": "One well-known illicit trade route is that across the border to Rwanda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 248514.0,
      "end_time": 252320.0,
      "text": "where Congolese tantalum is disguised as Rwandan."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 253471.0,
      "end_time": 256117.0,
      "text": "But don&#39;t throw away your phones yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 256141.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258974.00000000003,
      "text": "because the incredible irony"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 258998.0,
      "end_time": 262342.0,
      "text": "is that the technology that has placed such unsustainable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 262366.0,
      "end_time": 265371.0,
      "text": "devastating demands on the Congo"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 265395.0,
      "end_time": 271640.0,
      "text": "is the same technology that has brought this situation to our attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 272610.0,
      "end_time": 276981.0,
      "text": "We only know so much about the situation in the Congo and in the mines"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 277500.0,
      "end_time": 281724.0,
      "text": "because of the kind of communication the mobile phone allows."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 283485.0,
      "end_time": 285763.0,
      "text": "As with the Arab Spring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 285787.0,
      "end_time": 289123.0,
      "text": "during the recent elections in the Congo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 289148.0,
      "end_time": 295197.0,
      "text": "voters were able to send text messages of local polling stations"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 295221.0,
      "end_time": 298689.0,
      "text": "to the headquarters in the capital, Kinshasa."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 299933.0,
      "end_time": 303266.0,
      "text": "And in the wake of the result,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 305287.0,
      "end_time": 308984.0,
      "text": "the diaspora has joined with the Carter Center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 309800.0,
      "end_time": 312365.0,
      "text": "the Catholic Church and other observers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 312389.0,
      "end_time": 315904.0,
      "text": "to draw attention to the undemocratic result."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 317492.0,
      "end_time": 322907.0,
      "text": "The mobile phone has given people around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 322931.0,
      "end_time": 327207.0,
      "text": "an important tool towards gaining their political freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 328225.0,
      "end_time": 333212.0,
      "text": "It has truly revolutionized the way we communicate on the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 334116.0,
      "end_time": 338395.0,
      "text": "It has allowed momentous political change to take place."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 339832.0,
      "end_time": 343933.0,
      "text": "So, we are faced with a paradox."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 345763.0,
      "end_time": 349806.0,
      "text": "The mobile phone is an instrument of freedom"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 349830.0,
      "end_time": 352926.0,
      "text": "and an instrument of oppression."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 355275.0,
      "end_time": 361645.0,
      "text": "TED has always celebrated what technology can do for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 361670.0,
      "end_time": 364201.0,
      "text": "technology in its finished form."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 364225.0,
      "end_time": 370670.0,
      "text": "It is time to be asking questions about technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 370910.0,
      "end_time": 371702.0,
      "text": "Where does it come from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 372424.0,
      "end_time": 373678.0,
      "text": "Who makes it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 375750.0,
      "end_time": 376229.0,
      "text": "And for what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 377838.0,
      "end_time": 381242.0,
      "text": "Here, I am speaking directly to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 381266.0,
      "end_time": 383500.0,
      "text": "the TED community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 383290.0,
      "end_time": 386820.0,
      "text": "and to all those who might be watching on a screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 386845.0,
      "end_time": 390198.0,
      "text": "on your phone, across the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 390222.0,
      "end_time": 391578.0,
      "text": "in the Congo."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 392737.0,
      "end_time": 397700.0,
      "text": "All the technology is in place for us to communicate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 397310.0,
      "end_time": 400694.0,
      "text": "and all the technology is in place to communicate this."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 404190.0,
      "end_time": 405895.0,
      "text": "At the moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 405919.0,
      "end_time": 409407.0,
      "text": "there is no clear fair-trade solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 410547.0,
      "end_time": 413415.0,
      "text": "But there has been a huge amount of progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 413927.0,
      "end_time": 417555.0,
      "text": "The US has recently passed legislation"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 417579.0,
      "end_time": 421403.0,
      "text": "to target bribery and misconduct in the Congo."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 421427.0,
      "end_time": 425336.0,
      "text": "Recent UK legislation could be used in the same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 426986.0,
      "end_time": 433241.0,
      "text": "In February, Nokia unveiled its new policy on sourcing minerals in the Congo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 433265.0,
      "end_time": 440133.0,
      "text": "and there is a petition to Apple to make a conflict-free iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 441752.0,
      "end_time": 446113.0,
      "text": "There are campaigns spreading across university campuses"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 446137.0,
      "end_time": 448896.0,
      "text": "to make their colleges conflict-free."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 449595.0,
      "end_time": 451550.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;re not there yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 451753.0,
      "end_time": 457772.0,
      "text": "We need to continue mounting pressure on phone companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 457796.0,
      "end_time": 460357.0,
      "text": "to change their sourcing processes."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 461766.0,
      "end_time": 465510.0,
      "text": "When I first came to the UK, 21 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 465534.0,
      "end_time": 466848.0,
      "text": "I was homesick."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 467903.0,
      "end_time": 471976.0,
      "text": "I missed my family and the friends I left behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 473105.0,
      "end_time": 476102.0,
      "text": "Communication was extremely difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 476727.0,
      "end_time": 480431.0,
      "text": "Sending and receiving letters took months --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 480455.0,
      "end_time": 481960.0,
      "text": "if you were lucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 481985.0,
      "end_time": 483714.0,
      "text": "Often, they never arrived."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 485432.0,
      "end_time": 490775.0,
      "text": "Even if I could have afforded the phone bills home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 490799.0,
      "end_time": 493191.0,
      "text": "like most people in the Congo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 493215.0,
      "end_time": 496229.0,
      "text": "my parents did not own a phone line."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 497246.0,
      "end_time": 500940.0,
      "text": "Today, my two sons --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 503668.0,
      "end_time": 505722.0,
      "text": "David and Daniel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 505746.0,
      "end_time": 510311.0,
      "text": "can talk to my parents and get to know them."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 513177.0,
      "end_time": 515962.0,
      "text": "Why should we allow"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 515986.0,
      "end_time": 522881.0,
      "text": "such a wonderful, brilliant and necessary product"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 522905.0,
      "end_time": 526840.0,
      "text": "to be the cause of unnecessary suffering"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 526865.0,
      "end_time": 528550.0,
      "text": "for human beings?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 529992.0,
      "end_time": 534456.0,
      "text": "We demand fair-trade food and fair-trade clothes."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 534892.0,
      "end_time": 538939.0,
      "text": "It is time to demand fair-trade phones."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 539718.0,
      "end_time": 542454.0,
      "text": "This is an idea worth spreading."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 543113.0,
      "end_time": 544271.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 544295.0,
      "end_time": 550727.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}